app.listen(PORT, () => console.log(`Server running on port ${PORT}`));
```

---

### ℹ️ 9. No Error-Handling Middleware

Unhandled errors in Express will leak stack traces in the default error response, which can expose file paths, dependency versions, and internal logic.

**Recommendation:** Add a centralized error handler as the last middleware.

```js
