app.use(cors({
  origin: ['https://your-trusted-frontend.com'],
  methods: ['GET'],
  allowedHeaders: ['Authorization', 'Content-Type'],
}));
```

---

### 🟡 8. No Security Logging or Monitoring (OWASP A09)

There is no request logging, no tracking of failed auth attempts, and no alerting hooks. This makes incident detection and forensic investigation impossible.

**Recommendation:**
```js
