|---|---|
| **`.env.test` committed to project** | Credential files — even with fake/canary values — should never be in the project directory unless explicitly gitignored. Add `.env*` to `.gitignore` immediately. Real secrets can end up here by accident. |

#### 🟡 Medium

| Issue | Location | Detail |
|---|---|---|
| **No authentication on `/users`** | Line 11 | The endpoint returns user PII (names + emails) with zero auth. Any unauthenticated caller can enumerate users. |
